              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Fission fragments were detected using two",
                "large-area (16 cm X 11 cm) position-sensitive",
                "multiwire proportional counters (MWPCs), mounted on",
                "opposite arms of the scattering chamber. The forward",
                "and backward detectors were placed at distances of",
                "38 cm and 33 cm from the target, at angles of 45 degree",
                "and -115 degree with respect to the beam axis,",
                "respectively"
